## Completeness Checklist

- [ ] Gate ID and phase transition recorded correctly
- [ ] All expected artefacts listed in the Artefacts Reviewed table
- [ ] Evidence threshold assessment completed for each artefact
- [ ] All pass criteria from the gate contract assessed with explicit status
- [ ] Exactly one gate decision selected (PASS / FAIL / WAIVED)
- [ ] Rationale for decision is substantive and auditable
- [ ] If conditional pass: conditions table populated with owners and deadlines
- [ ] If WAIVED: Waiver Justification section fully completed including risk acceptance
- [ ] Next Steps table populated
- [ ] Sign-off section completed by all required parties
